text: Kinnih immay Nabiyow ku Rabbi kah nacroore maray kaal yeemeneeh kay farmoytit kataate Yallih inkittinaanel itta mawaa, woh kay fayxiiy kay mekla, usuk ken kah ginem meqe maraa kee uma maray sissini yakkeeninkeh iyyaanama, Nabiyow ku Rabbih qangaraa kee kay mekla gaba kalteh, diggah anu Jahannam gira jinnii kee sinaamak inkih kibeyyo iyyaanamal
